Package phase10

Class Summary
Card This class contains all of the information for each playing card for the Phase 10 game.
CardColorComparator This is used to compare cards to each other and determine the order they should be in.
CardValueComparator This is used to compare cards to each other and determine the order they should be in.
GameManager This class manages the back end functions such as save/load/new game
Hand This class contains and manages the cards in each player's hand
Phase10 This class contains and manages the information for each Phase 10 game
PhaseGroup This class contains all of the information for each phase group that is laid down in a round.
Player This class contains all of the information for each player for the Phase 10 game.
Round This class contains and manages the information for each round
